show.description: Eve, a humble cleaner with only a high school education, accidentally spends a night with the enigmatic CEO, Mr. Noa. Mistaken identity leads Noa to believe his partner was the glamorous Layla —until fate intervenes with an arranged marriage. To his shock, his bride is none other than Eve, and amidst secrets and misunderstandings, an unexpected love begins to bloom.
